    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入残酷的中世纪战场，生存是唯一的选择！在这个充满动作的海浪生存游戏中，你将与无情的敌人作战，每一波都比上一波更强大。但你并不孤单——利用独特的超能力来摧毁你的敌人，并饲养具有特殊能力的猪来帮助你战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>激烈的海浪式战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与无数波中世纪战士作战，每个战士都有独特的力量和能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超能力</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >释放毁灭性的力量来扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/43015b628b783bd64f54963dd98d5dfb.poster.avif?t=1767683112\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/43015b628b783bd64f54963dd98d5dfb.webm?t=1767683112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/43015b628b783bd64f54963dd98d5dfb.mp4?t=1767683112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>猪繁殖系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >饲养和增强具有特殊能力的猪，与你并肩作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/d1afe79041eca05f6612aa15019c9e68.poster.avif?t=1767683112\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/d1afe79041eca05f6612aa15019c9e68.webm?t=1767683112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/d1afe79041eca05f6612aa15019c9e68.mp4?t=1767683112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新能力，提高你的属性，并定制你的战斗策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/d0d53d12e8b7ec56b1409d72a1199029.poster.avif?t=1767683112\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/d0d53d12e8b7ec56b1409d72a1199029.webm?t=1767683112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313330/extras/d0d53d12e8b7ec56b1409d72a1199029.mp4?t=1767683112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>强大的敌人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对越来越难对付的敌人，考验你的技能和适应能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>你能在猛攻中幸存下来，成为终极中世纪战士吗？战斗、适应和征服！</strong></i></p>",
